casebody.data:
MCCONNELL
v.
DUDLEY 2018-0377 Supreme Court of Ohio. August 1, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Appeal accepted on proposition of law No. I. Cross-appeal not accepted. Kennedy and DeWine, JJ., would accept the appeal on all propositions of law. Fischer, J., would also accept proposition of law No. II and would accept the cross-appeal. O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, J., dissent. DeGenaro, J., not participating.
